{"tid":642751,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"土地大辯論　數字說真相","createTime":"2018-04-26T04:29:56.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-26T04:55:39.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"736d0321cd66321b712866f2d48d3c75f6c25da9","tid":642751,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-26T04:29:56.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180426/20373343?_ga=2.74678930.1029761066.1520127978-1555213041.1517019171\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180426%2F20373343%3F_ga%3D2.74678930.1029761066.1520127978-1555213041.1517019171&d=2FAxEgbFnn6Qln%2BSqq5Whf7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=905c22ee\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180426%2F20373343%3F_ga%3D2.74678930.1029761066.1520127978-1555213041.1517019171&h=20ac7a16\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180426/20373343?_ga=2.74678930.1029761066.1520127978-1555213041.1517019171</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年04月26日 <br />\n<br />\n土地大辯論　數字說真相<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180426/large/a0901a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180426%2Flarge%2Fa0901a.gif&h=ad124204&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■本土研究社早前推算，橫台山有多達71公頃棕地。資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n【供地真相】<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】土地供應專責小組今日展開諮詢，預料將提出十多個土地供應選項，並分為短中期措施、中長期措施及概念性建議，應發展哪些土地。究竟棕地有多少發展潛力？公私營合作發展農地，對哪一間地產商最有利？收回粉嶺高爾夫球場，可建多少個單位？《蘋果》拆解主要土地供應建議，尋找供地真相。<br />\n<br />\n記者：林偉聰<br />\n <br />\n　<br />\n <img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180426/large/a0901b.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180426%2Flarge%2Fa0901b.gif&h=239d45e7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n　<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180426/large/a0901c.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180426%2Flarge%2Fa0901c.gif&h=ef374579&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180426/large/a0901d.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180426%2Flarge%2Fa0901d.gif&h=e5f24c60&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180426/large/a0901e.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180426%2Flarge%2Fa0901e.gif&h=29584cfe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n　  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n區晞旻：政府將村民與市民對立<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n警認睇漏南生圍縱火片段<br />\n<br />\n發展粉嶺高球場勢遇政治阻力<br />\n<br />\n家族公司擁高球場旁土地　何君堯認漏報<br />\n<br />\n區晞旻：政府將村民與市民對立<br />\n<br />\n斥政府覓地「跑數」只顧拆村黃浩銘促收發展商農地建公屋"},{"pid":"7b73783c49224b33aedb188840af83d7e388533b","tid":642751,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-26T04:55:39.000Z","msg":"泛民打手LIKLN<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/26/125537_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F26%2F125537_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=5729473c&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}